1. *Umalo* nisam zaboravio da uzmem novčanik prije nego što sam otišao. (I almost forgot to take my wallet before I left.)

2. *Umalo* se nisam spotakla po stepenicama. (I almost tripped on the stairs.)

3. *Umalo* nisam prešla na druge strane ulice pre nego što je zelena traka za pešake izbledela. (I almost crossed to the other side of the street before the pedestrian crossing light went out.)

4. *Umalo* nisam zaboravio da platim račun pre nego što sam napustio restoran. (I almost forgot to pay the bill before I left the restaurant.)

5. *Umalo* nisam prekršio zakon pre nego što sam shvatio da on postoji. (I almost broke the law before I realized it existed.)